This is the README file for Locale::Hebrew, a module implementing
bidirectional Hebrew support for Perl.

* Installation

Locale::Hebrew uses the standard perl module install process:

cpansign -v		# see SIGNATURE for details
perl Makefile.PL
make
make test
make install

